=== Code Execution Task ===

==== Functionality ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.task.CodeExecutionTask
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}

==== Configuration Settings ====

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.task.CodeExecutionTask
| type = CONFIGURATION
}}

==== Quick guide ====

This task can invoke methods 
which are normally called by the [[Help:CodeExecution | Code Execution Widget]]. 
The parameter (un)marshalling works the same way as for the [[Help:APITask]].
Note that the CodeExecutionContext parameter is not supported and can only be
passed as a null value. See the example below:

==== Example ====

Deleting all incoming and outgoing statements of a resource:

<source>
clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.util.ResourceControl
method = deleteResource
args = System:null
args = <http://www.fluidops.com/resource/DeleteMe>
</source>
